<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Suakliana</author>
<hymn_number>95</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw hehpihna ka gen thiem puoh na'n ka thip thei puoi,
 Lei leh van Lalpa lopi leh thiengtho hawih zie,
 Hallelujah, I thiem dandan bek un thil hitiu.

[V2]
 Thiengtho, thiengtho, thiengtho,
 Thiengtho I Lalpen chu;
 Thiengtho thiengtho, thiengtho,
 Ei Hukdampa ahi.

[V3]
 2. Aw hehpihna ka gen seng puoi, aw a za na e,
 Khawvel thimna leh lungkham na mei zing mahleh;
 A nang diek puoi gawtmun inle aw a vak na e.

[V4]
 3. Hallelujah, Hallelujah, aw a vak na e,
 Zion vak chunga thienthona la hawih a sau;
 A pak la tuipi kinawk guolin a hai thei puoi.</lyrics>
<title>Thiengtho, Thiengtho</title>
</song>